WEBVTT

00:05:28.300 --> 00:05:30.810
the voice of women.

00:05:31.240 --> 00:05:33.480
I recently released a film,

00:05:33.480 --> 00:05:36.480
because I have the power now,

00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:38.560
which was called
"Lipstick under my burqa".

00:05:40.150 --> 00:05:44.710
(Applause and cheers)

00:05:44.810 --> 00:05:46.740
Actually, in that I got criticism

00:05:46.760 --> 00:05:51.640
about how one who makes such traditional
TV shows is now releasing a sex film.

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:58.119
I said sex and tradition
are two aspects of the same woman.

00:05:58.120 --> 00:06:04.879
Whether a story is about Tulsi, Ushaji
or Silk, who are we to disrespect her?